  Windows, Messages, SysUtils, Variants, Classes, Graphics, Controls, Forms,
  Dialogs, ComCtrls, zAntivirus, wintrust, zSharedFunctions, zKeyloggerHunter,
  zLogSystem, zAVKernel;

type
